Posted By: Marc Del Percio
Hello,

I am finally down to the last 3 that I need for the set.  Thanks to everybody on the board that I have traded with/purchased from over the past few years of collecting this set.  I'm looking for the following T206 cards:



Keeler (with bat)

Kiernan

Paige


I prefer them in low condition...even beaters are fine for now.  Graded or raw.  I'm hoping to stay in the range of $100 or less for the Keeler and $50-$60 or so for the Kiernan and Paige.  If you are interested in trading, I also have over 100 mostly low grade T205's and T206's available including many HOF's and short prints.  Thanks for looking and please send any offers.  I will respond to all.
